Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.44,0:00:09.40,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Kagami Yoshimizu Theater"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.27,0:00:05.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, let's do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.88,0:00:06.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.88,0:00:07.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grr!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.52,0:00:09.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Quit screwing around and start!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.40,0:00:12.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The ambiguous 3cm?\NDoes that mean it's plushy? Wait!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.40,0:00:15.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The wrapping is a uniform, argh,\Nit's not an act, pooh{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.57,0:00:17.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Gotta do your best, gotta just do it{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.29,0:00:18.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's time to catch 'n' release, eek{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.91,0:00:20.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Between sweat (whoop)\NSweat (whoop){\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.73,0:00:23.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Darlin', darlin', freeze! {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.59,0:00:30.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kinda lethargic,\Nsomething's kinda comin' out{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.00,0:00:31.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I love you... Oh wait,\None of those was different{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.92,0:00:33.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Worrywarts, high metal bars {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.20,0:00:34.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Tasty thoughts... And that's enough!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.93,0:00:36.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The heated body of that\Nflying you-know-who{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.72,0:00:38.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's what you call a normal girlie{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.43,0:00:39.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Am I the only one surprised? {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.60,0:00:40.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Seconds on pork-bone broth ramen\Nwith wire-hard noodles{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.77,0:00:41.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Da da da da da {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.98,0:00:49.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Pom-poms cheer squad{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.77,0:00:51.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Let's get cherry pie {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.37,0:00:52.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Happy fun welcoming party {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.87,0:00:54.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Look up! Sensation{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.46,0:00:57.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yeah! Feeling of existence,\Ndot dot small planet{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.58,0:00:59.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Collided and it melted away,\Nin total awe{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.20,0:01:00.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Go all out to sing, shi-ranger!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.91,0:01:02.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Take it away! {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.12,0:01:06.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I should be the one who'll be\Nlaughing in the end{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.49,0:01:13.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Because I have the sailor suit\N← This is my conclusion{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.51,0:01:15.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's only Monday! {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.82,0:01:19.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Already in a bad mood? What to do?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.37,0:01:26.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I really prefer the summer outfits\N← kya! Wah! Good! (cute!) < 3{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.14,0:01:29.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Until we approach 3 pixels,\Nno hesitations please ★{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.39,0:01:31.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Do your best, be energetic {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.02,0:01:33.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My darlin', darlin' please! {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.89,0:01:37.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... we're going to start\Na long vacation tomorrow,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.48,0:01:39.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but don't forget your\Nposition as a student,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.56,0:01:41.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and spend your days in moderation.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.53,0:01:43.04,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Various things to watch out for \Nduring summer vacation"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.53,0:01:43.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.33,0:01:45.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Many students get all worked up\Nduring this season,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.95,0:01:48.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and cause a lot of trouble to\Ntheir neighborhood societies.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.94,0:01:51.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I, as your teacher,\Nam very worried about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.93,0:01:54.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, make sure you don't\Ncause any problems!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.82,0:01:59.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, if you\Ncause any problems,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.15,0:02:02.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you're going to kill my vacation\Nas well, so I'm begging you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.62,0:02:04.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is no good...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.52,0:02:07.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Famous Shooter"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.52,0:02:10.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're finally on vacation now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.63,0:02:12.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's reassuring to think\Nthat I don't have
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.56,0:02:14.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to see your face each and every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.70,0:02:16.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sis...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.72,0:02:19.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, even though it's vacation,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.58,0:02:22.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to see our teacher\Nalmost every day anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.30,0:02:24.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why? You have summer\Nclasses or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.66,0:02:27.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We form parties in our\N'net game and stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.58,0:02:29.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's something about that...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.02,0:02:30.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,'Net game?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.06,0:02:32.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our teacher is a wiz and I'm a tank,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.59,0:02:34.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so when we pair up and I pull stuff,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.92,0:02:37.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it's pretty good in terms\Nof both xp and money.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.55,0:02:39.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Though I'm always the busy one,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.96,0:02:43.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and all our teacher does is click\Non one of the AoE skills.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.80,0:02:46.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The other day, I pulled a ton of mobs
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.01,0:02:48.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,only to find our teacher had\Nfallen asleep at the keyboard,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.59,0:02:51.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and it took me all day to earn\Nmy death penalty back...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.19,0:02:55.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, can you at least\Nspeak in Japanese?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.11,0:02:59.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Morning...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.04,0:03:01.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so hot today for so\Nearly in the morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.79,0:03:04.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Morning. Your hair is\Nquite amazing right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.65,0:03:06.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Sis, how about we turn on\Nthe air conditioning?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.91,0:03:08.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There you go again.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.52,0:03:10.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't rely on stuff like that so quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.68,0:03:12.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Use a fan or something and\Nbear with it, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.76,0:03:13.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.75,0:03:14.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.38,0:03:17.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It gets pretty cool with just a fan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.96,0:03:19.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.29,0:03:21.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm hot.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.60,0:03:24.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I get tired when\NI keep fanning myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.64,0:03:28.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And when you stop using a fan,\Ndon't you feel even hotter?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.27,0:03:30.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, well, I knew that...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.96,0:03:32.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you can try a little harder.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.46,0:03:38.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are wearing yukatas together.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.06,0:03:39.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yup, yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.12,0:03:42.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, our obis are\Nsimple pre-tied ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.96,0:03:44.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The ones you can put on easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.58,0:03:47.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's difficult to put a kimono on,\Neven if it's just a yukata.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.04,0:03:50.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miyuki's obi is tied up\Ntraditionally, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.67,0:03:52.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just like you'd expect.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.33,0:03:56.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I had the person\Nat the shop do it for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.24,0:03:59.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, even I find tying\Nan obi to be difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.96,0:04:01.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.58,0:04:05.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Konata is wearing a proper one\Nas well... much to my surprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.59,0:04:07.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you get help at the store as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.95,0:04:11.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, Dad tied it for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.10,0:04:13.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.55,0:04:15.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.56,0:04:20.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How come her dad\Nknows how to tie one?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.83,0:04:24.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, it's Konata!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.17,0:04:27.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone from the police?\NYou know her, Konata?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.76,0:04:30.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Yui is a relative of mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.09,0:04:31.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.92,0:04:33.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Oh, hello there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.19,0:04:34.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Nice to meet you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.33,0:04:36.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't wreak too much havoc!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.43,0:04:40.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen to what these older girls say,\Nand go home early, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.67,0:04:44.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, no, we're all in the same grade!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.67,0:04:46.39,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Older girls"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.64,0:04:46.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make Konata the standard!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.39,0:04:48.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're all in the same grade.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.73,0:04:49.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.68,0:04:52.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, sorry, that really surprises me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.46,0:04:54.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, your physiques are so\Ndifferent that I couldn't help it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.17,0:04:56.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.19,0:05:01.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that aside, kids these days\Nreally are well-endowed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.11,0:05:04.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, like I said, don't make\NKonata the standard!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.09,0:05:05.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're all normal!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.99,0:05:08.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, it's a shooting gallery!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.53,0:05:11.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you good at stuff like this, Yui?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.31,0:05:15.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To tell you the truth, I'm so good
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.72,0:05:18.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that they call me\NSharpshooter Yui at the station!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.78,0:05:20.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can shoot five rounds in\Nthree seconds and nail pinheads!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.88,0:05:23.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can draw a peace mark\Non a paper target's head!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.35,0:05:27.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then try it out! Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.63,0:05:29.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.44,0:05:30.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The shooting gallery uses a rifle?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.99,0:05:32.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a surprise!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.96,0:05:35.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I use pistols.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.60,0:05:37.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excited! Excited!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.65,0:05:49.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Narumi! What's got you so fired up?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.32,0:05:50.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're still on the job!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.41,0:05:52.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, patrol, patrol...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.48,0:05:55.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Getting back on hand...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.34,0:05:58.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mister, the stuff lined up over there...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.60,0:06:00.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we hit a target, we can get\Nany one of them?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.99,0:06:03.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Any of them are okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.53,0:06:04.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Any of them?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.57,0:06:05.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, any of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.91,0:06:13.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, missy, I'm not a prize.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.54,0:06:15.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When you talk about\Na summer festival,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.10,0:06:16.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you can't forget the shaved ice!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.70,0:06:18.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's hot, too. Let's go eat some.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.73,0:06:21.40,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Melon" "Lemon" "Strawberry"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.73,0:06:21.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.40,0:06:29.24,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Blue Hawaii" "Melon" "Lemon"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.79,0:06:25.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can understand strawberry, \Nlemon, and melon flavors...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.36,0:06:29.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But what fruit is Blue Hawaii? \NWhat kinda flavor is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.07,0:06:34.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The flavor would be\NBlue Hawaii, I would think?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.66,0:06:37.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's true...\NThat's how it would end up...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.29,0:06:42.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so, Miyuki-{\i1}san{\i0}, do you know\Nwhat Blue Hawaii is?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.01,0:06:44.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Blue Hawaii, was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.89,0:06:46.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see... Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.24,0:06:48.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe it's a song...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.32,0:06:50.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Blue... That's not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.13,0:06:53.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That I do not know.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.08,0:06:58.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry I can't be of use.\NI'll look it up later.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.04,0:07:00.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, please do!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.08,0:07:03.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--I'd think that it's named after\Na juice or some kind of sweets...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.33,0:07:06.22,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,--No, the one who wants to know\Nshould be looking it up, not Miyuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.22,0:07:10.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, about that Blue Hawaii...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.57,0:07:15.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The name comes from a cocktail\Nof the same name and color.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.74,0:07:18.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The cocktail was named after\Nand pays homage to
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.62,0:07:20.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the movie {\i1}Blue Hawaii{\i0}, so they say.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.58,0:07:24.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's what it was...\NIt's a good reference.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.91,0:07:27.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When Tsukasa teaches me something,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.64,0:07:31.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,for some reason, I feel like\NI've really been defeated!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.29,0:07:34.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just realized that I don't\Nhave much money left.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.89,0:07:37.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These booths aren't cheap.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.50,0:07:40.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have to think before\Nyou spend, you know? Geez...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.43,0:07:45.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But during festivals, you kinda\Ngo with the atmosphere
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.05,0:07:47.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and can't help but to get\Nyour hands on all sorts of stuff!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.60,0:07:48.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.69,0:07:50.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the same illusion as not thinking
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.64,0:07:53.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that a {\i1}doujinshi {\i0}is expensive\Nwhen you're at Comiket.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.36,0:07:55.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't realize just how much\Nyou've spent until later.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.32,0:07:56.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As I've been saying,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.09,0:07:58.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't understand when\Nyou talk about that genre!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.33,0:08:00.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You get all tired lining up\Nfrom early in the morning,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.84,0:08:03.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and the West Hall is so\Nfar away from East Hall...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.20,0:08:05.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't understand what\Nyou're talking about!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.83,0:08:09.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I love cotton candy!\NIt's so fluffy and sweet!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.24,0:08:14.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not a kid!\NCalm down when you eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.40,0:08:20.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no fun doing that stuff\Nwith another girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.56,0:08:21.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.88,0:08:25.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't we have that\Nthing they call romance?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.26,0:08:28.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're at a summer festival\Nand wearing yukatas, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.56,0:08:30.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If this was a dating sim,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.00,0:08:32.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you'd think there'd be at least\None flag up right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.57,0:08:33.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Flag?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.56,0:08:37.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That, and an event scene.\NIn yukatas, and outside...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.64,0:08:39.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, okay, that's enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.81,0:08:42.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kagami-{\i1}san{\i0}, you're not\Ngoing to play anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.25,0:08:44.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's a nice occasion after all,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.94,0:08:47.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I guess I'll do some\Ngoldfish scooping.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.79,0:08:55.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't even tried anything.\NWhy are they running?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.48,0:08:57.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They instinctively feel that\Nyou're vicious, Kagami,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.42,0:08:59.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and that's why they're running away.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.99,0:09:02.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Finally, the evidence is coming out.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.35,0:09:07.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, over there, there's one over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.88,0:09:10.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right. Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.41,0:09:13.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gotcha!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.69,0:09:17.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! I've caught one!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.00,0:09:18.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing! Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.81,0:09:22.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take care of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.08,0:09:26.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take really good care of it.\NRight, Gyopi-{\i1}chan{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.92,0:09:31.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yo! You're all together!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.21,0:09:33.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard there was a festival\Ngoing on around here,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.74,0:09:36.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and thought I might as well come.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.04,0:09:37.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I love festivals.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.87,0:09:41.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you come here together today\Nwith your boyfriend or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.96,0:09:44.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course not. There ain't one.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.49,0:09:48.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So there isn't even a fragment\Nof romance around us after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.96,0:09:50.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just as we expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.84,0:09:52.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We see each other again!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.15,0:09:54.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even more people?\NLooks like you're having fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.76,0:09:56.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey there!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.92,0:10:03.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This time, you really have\Na well-endowed girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.63,0:10:04.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.59,0:10:06.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's our homeroom teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.33,0:10:08.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, I jumped to the conclusion
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.32,0:10:10.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that you were one of\Ntheir classmates...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.30,0:10:11.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.61,0:10:13.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yui is a relative of mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.39,0:10:15.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As you can see, she's a cop.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.00,0:10:18.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, since today is a summer festival,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.91,0:10:21.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have looking-around duty.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.05,0:10:23.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, in this heat!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.06,0:10:26.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Duty? You're having so much fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.09,0:10:30.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you on duty as well, ma'am?\NLike, looking around?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.97,0:10:33.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I was bored, so I was\Njust wandering around...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.82,0:10:36.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so jealous! If I was off duty,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.35,0:10:39.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I could have wandered around\Nby myself and played a little!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.03,0:10:43.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, you're having enough fun as it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.47,0:10:46.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So are you alone as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.54,0:10:48.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I'm alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.04,0:10:50.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.67,0:10:50.54,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Single"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.25,0:10:52.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Husband's on a commuter marriage"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.31,0:10:59.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Lucky Star{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.43,0:11:05.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As for vinegar, I would\Nrecommend balsamic vinegar,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.00,0:11:09.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--but if you don't have any, whatever you \Nhave at home, such as rice vinegar, will do.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.67,0:11:09.43,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,--Balsamic vinegar...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.81,0:11:11.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Balsamic vinegar...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.36,0:11:14.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Balsamic vinegar!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.52,0:11:16.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,During summer vacation,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.32,0:11:19.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you get kind of bored because\Nthere's nothing to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.58,0:11:21.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't help but get a little lazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.12,0:11:24.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since you say that much,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.60,0:11:27.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you won't be asking me later to\Nshow you my homework, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.96,0:11:34.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's true. Yeah. It is cute after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.73,0:11:39.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How it's kinda pudgy and roly-poly\Nand how it looks like a frog.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.08,0:11:43.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, yeah. Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.97,0:11:47.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see, so it's depleted uranium.\NThat's amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.44,0:11:52.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, if I talk on the phone\Nfor too long, I'll get scolded.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.27,0:11:56.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! Talk to you later!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.90,0:11:59.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was talking with Kona-{\i1}chan{\i0},
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.92,0:12:03.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And asked her how summer vacation\Nends up being pretty boring.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.39,0:12:06.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She said she wasn't bored because
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.16,0:12:09.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,she was playing\Nall the games that had piled up.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.08,0:12:13.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess some people have\Na very fulfilling summer vacation.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.43,0:12:15.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I should do something too!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.79,0:12:18.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that's a good thing\Nin itself, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.64,0:12:21.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm telling you, do your homework\Non top of all that!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.52,0:12:24.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really, each and every time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.05,0:12:27.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna pull one.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.18,0:12:34.39,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,"Konakona: I'm gonna pull one."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.76,0:12:36.90,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,"Yamanka: OK"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.52,0:12:42.94,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,"Gatongo: All right, let's do this! (rotfl)"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.39,0:12:35.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Debuff, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.39,0:12:42.94,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,"Konakona: Debuff plz."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.90,0:12:42.94,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,"Your friend Nanakon has logged in."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.32,0:12:40.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, our teacher logged in.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.12,0:12:43.90,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Konakona: Hello."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.12,0:12:44.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.90,0:12:49.16,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,"Nanakon: Yo! (^3^)/"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.15,0:12:49.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe it's because it's vacation, but\Nthe connection speed is really good.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.16,0:12:54.87,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,"Nanakon: Well, yeah (lol)"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.48,0:12:53.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have some time,\Nshall we go grind some things?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.79,0:12:56.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm in the cave near Chovron Village.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.87,0:13:01.84,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,"Nanakon: All right, I'll go, I'll go! (>w<)b\NIt's time for a wiz to step up!"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.63,0:13:01.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll be waiting near the gate.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.84,0:13:08.01,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,"Nanakon: That's fine, but did you\Ndo your homework? (-_-)"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.06,0:13:06.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.01,0:13:12.52,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,"Nanakon: Have you been cooped up\Ninside your house? (-_-)"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.52,0:13:16.60,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,"Nanakon: Don't forget about the day\Nyou have to come to school (-3-)y-~~~"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.60,0:13:19.02,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,"Nanakon: One more thing, even though it's\Nvacation, don't stay up too late or sleep in too much."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.32,0:13:22.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ma'am, stop talking about real life
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.27,0:13:26.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,every day inside the 'net game world!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.18,0:13:31.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's like Kagami\Nscolding me every day...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.91,0:13:35.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heya! It's hot again today!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.79,0:13:38.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, welcome! Come on in!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.42,0:13:39.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.18,0:13:45.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You got the fan out.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.05,0:13:46.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, because it's hot.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.87,0:13:48.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chill out there for a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.68,0:13:54.98,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Ah..."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.80,0:13:58.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought she'd do it.\NI was positive that she'd do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.14,0:14:01.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning...\NOh, Kona-{\i1}chan {\i0}is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.32,0:14:02.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S'up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.19,0:14:06.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not "good morning."\NWhat time do you think it is?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.76,0:14:11.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In any case, it's hot out.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.59,0:14:15.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.12,0:14:16.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, everyone usually does it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.78,0:14:18.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.16,0:14:20.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you were doing it\Nthis morning, Kagami.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.10,0:14:22.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.00,0:14:24.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was seen...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.80,0:14:27.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Comp-Fest seems\Nto be pretty popular.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.45,0:14:28.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.68,0:14:31.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When you collect the entry tickets\Nthat come with the graphic novels
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.50,0:14:33.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,of series from this magazine,\Nand send them in,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.93,0:14:36.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you get a limited edition\NQUO card in no time!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.68,0:14:38.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.16,0:14:40.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I also end up taking those graphic\Nnovels to the cash register,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.25,0:14:42.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,as if I were drawn to the cashier...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.99,0:14:46.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were going on about\NQUO cards the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.25,0:14:48.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really, Japanese people are so weak
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.16,0:14:50.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,when it comes to giveaways\Nor limited edition items.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.48,0:14:52.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why it's rudimentary to buy
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.46,0:14:55.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,one to store, one to look at,\Nand one to spread the gospel!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.36,0:14:58.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! There's no doubt\Nthat yours is a special case!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.44,0:15:00.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Most people don't think like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.30,0:15:04.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sometimes you forget who you lent\Nit to, and end up buying a new one.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.03,0:15:05.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't forget!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.17,0:15:08.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so, I'd like to ask you\Nabout that usual thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.76,0:15:09.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, homework.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.98,0:15:11.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Again?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.08,0:15:13.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll teach you all the bits\Nthat you don't understand,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.56,0:15:15.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so why don't you do it\Nby yourself for a change?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.68,0:15:19.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Balsamic vinegar...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.29,0:15:23.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kagami, show me how to do this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.52,0:15:25.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, this here is...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.54,0:15:33.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kagami, I don't understand\Nfrom here to here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.97,0:15:37.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, close.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.29,0:15:40.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Kagami, this bit...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.50,0:15:42.12,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,--You aren't even going \Nto try thinking, are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.86,0:15:47.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.55,0:15:48.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that really so?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.88,0:15:51.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I don't understand\Nanything from here on...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.90,0:15:53.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You aren't thinking after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.40,0:15:57.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the end, she wouldn't teach me...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.22,0:16:00.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! I'm here to visit!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.60,0:16:03.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Yui, good timing!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.68,0:16:06.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Show me how to do this part!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.22,0:16:09.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Math homework... let's see,\Nwhich part? Leave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.32,0:16:15.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, as a police officer\Nlooking after a good girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.80,0:16:19.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no good to rely on\Nother people all the time!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.44,0:16:30.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't get this stuff, it's such a pain...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.43,0:16:33.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you don't get it,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.00,0:16:35.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,just scribble down something\Nthat sounds right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.99,0:16:38.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, the point of homework\Nis to just turn something in.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.60,0:16:41.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I see! Good thinking!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.10,0:16:45.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that line of yours earlier\Nseems so superficial now,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.84,0:16:48.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,because doing that,\Nit won't do me good.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.60,0:16:50.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I did the same thing myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.44,0:16:53.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so tired...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.87,0:16:58.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think I'll take a breather and\Nplay the 'net game for a little bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.55,0:17:03.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure thirty minutes of\Nsolo grinding should be good.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.72,0:17:05.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it's only thirty minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.51,0:17:13.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm solo grinding...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.88,0:17:19.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In this world...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.52,0:17:25.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Getting stronger...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.00,0:17:37.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A rare drop...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.45,0:17:38.41,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"You have obtained\NEnchanted Blade Laevatein."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.41,0:17:39.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Laevatein?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.41,0:17:43.50,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Something like this"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.98,0:17:43.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never seen anyone who had it!\NThat's ultra-rare!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.64,0:17:47.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got the sword Laeva!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.96,0:17:50.46,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,"Yamanka: Serious?!? (@@)"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.46,0:17:52.46,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,"Gatongo: Oh man (rotfl) Grats (rotfl)"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.46,0:17:55.97,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,"Yamanka: I'll go over there right now,\Nshow me show me! (>w<)/"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.97,0:17:59.47,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,"Matchy: Let's celebrate. We can gather all the\Nclan members together, and try it out. O(^^)o"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.47,0:18:04.06,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,"Gatongo: All-nighter guaranteed! (rotfl) I'm (lol)\Nfeeling (lol) totally (lol) Energetic (lol) now (rotfl)"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.06,0:18:05.06,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,"Konakona: OK, come-come."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.06,0:18:08.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, where should I\Nbreak this thing in?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.12,0:18:10.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, everyone's so into going.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.43,0:18:12.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know, I'll celebrate by stocking up\Non the high-quality potions,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.94,0:18:14.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and give them out to everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.17,0:18:17.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,First, I'll go back to town...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.49,0:18:21.49,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Math II"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.02,0:18:20.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is going to get really busy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.33,0:18:23.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Lucky Star{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.49,0:18:27.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Lucky Channel{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.04,0:18:28.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Morning Luckies!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.79,0:18:31.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Akira Kogami, your navigator!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.45,0:18:34.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Time passes by so quickly, {\i1}Lucky\NChannel {\i0}is already on its fifth show!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.78,0:18:38.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to do my best, and put\Neven more enthusiasm into it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.47,0:18:40.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And as usual, my assistant is
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.50,0:18:43.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,getting more lines in the actual\Nepisode, and letting it go to his head...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.31,0:18:50.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...no, doing very well...\NIt's Minoru Shiraishi-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.09,0:18:51.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Clap, clap, clap!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.02,0:18:53.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I have no intention\Nof letting it go to my head.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.99,0:18:58.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I'm Minoru Shiraishi,\Nthe assistant. Hope to do well.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.82,0:19:03.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, we receive mountains\Nof letters each week!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.15,0:19:07.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Today, I'd like to introduce a letter\Nsent by Mr. USS Gatoh in Tokyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.21,0:19:11.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is he a NE__? This one person\Nsent fifty letters!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.42,0:19:14.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure he's a poor,\Npathetic individual!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.30,0:19:16.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, the letter goes:
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.56,0:19:19.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello to Miss Akira and Mr. Minoru!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.20,0:19:23.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the main show, Konata seems\Nto be playing a 'net game,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.04,0:19:26.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but do you play games like\Nthis as well, Miss Akira?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.08,0:19:29.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, I role-play as a {\i1}nekama{\i0},
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.95,0:19:32.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and have a very\Nfulfilling everyday life.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.44,0:19:34.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, how painful!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.73,0:19:37.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,'Net game... a network game, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.87,0:19:40.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unfortunately, I've never\Nplayed those things.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.45,0:19:43.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. But you're better off\Nnot playing them.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.41,0:19:45.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You sure cut it down again today...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.55,0:19:48.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.59,0:19:50.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are so many people\Nwho get totally hooked,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.84,0:19:53.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and leave their real lives\Nbehind somewhere else...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.24,0:19:55.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There was a period of time\Nwhere I was pretty bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.63,0:19:58.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I had time,\NI would be logged in,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.65,0:20:01.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and would go on and on\Nto grind or to PKK...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.56,0:20:03.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was when I was young.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.34,0:20:05.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When you were young?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.16,0:20:07.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or rather, there are all sorts of\Nterms that you just mentioned
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.93,0:20:09.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,which I don't understand...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.97,0:20:12.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're better off not knowing them.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.12,0:20:16.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever, it's not like the whole\Naudience will understand, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.73,0:20:19.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In any case, you had been\Nplaying in the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.50,0:20:23.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, Akira-{\i1}sama{\i0}, do you have any\Nmemories about games of the sort?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.55,0:20:26.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yes, memories! I have some!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.27,0:20:30.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I was a beginner,\NI didn't understand many things,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.06,0:20:34.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and was in trouble when all sorts\Nof nice veterans helped me out!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.38,0:20:38.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They gave me lots of really\Nexpensive armor and rare items,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.80,0:20:40.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and I was so thrilled!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.35,0:20:43.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.42,0:20:47.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's very fun, so everyone\Nshould try playing them!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.47,0:20:50.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's already time to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.11,0:20:51.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye-nee!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.97,0:20:54.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, we'll see you next episode.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.98,0:20:58.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or rather, when you're in games\Nlike that, you're extremely popular.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.04,0:21:03.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Akira-{\i1}sama{\i0}?\NIs something the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.13,0:21:05.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Page 38, cut 12...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.71,0:21:06.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.01,0:21:09.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who the hell is Yutaka, dammit?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.15,0:21:10.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Is this where you get mad today?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.86,0:21:12.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--I'm telling you, I'm Akira!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.79,0:21:13.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Yes, that is true, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.19,0:21:14.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Whoever is in charge, come out here!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.52,0:21:15.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Wait, director! Director!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.79,0:21:17.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--No, the producer is better! The producer!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.36,0:21:17.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--You know damn well!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.98,0:21:20.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, please, Akira-{\i1}sama{\i0}, please calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.62,0:21:22.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Please, I beg you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.92,0:21:22.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--While we're at it...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.11,0:21:22.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.54,0:21:24.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's take the name Minoru Shiraishi
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.88,0:21:27.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and turn it into\Nsomething else... Like Su--
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.20,0:21:31.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kagamin, you're so cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.96,0:21:33.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're just saying that!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.36,0:21:36.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, Tsukasa or Miyuki,\Nwhich of you will go next?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.00,0:21:36.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.73,0:21:39.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Again?! When the hell did you...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.04,0:21:42.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys weren't putting any in.\NIt's a waste!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.36,0:21:45.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry. I'm still picking a song,\Nso wait just a bit more for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.08,0:21:46.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.08,0:21:47.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.84,0:21:50.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Konata's song can fill up\Nthe spare time anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.76,0:21:55.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I know this one!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.34,0:21:58.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazingly enough, this selection is\Nfrom a mainstream series for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.54,0:22:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ The best! ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.00,0:22:01.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ Sparking! ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.90,0:22:07.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ Break through the shining clouds,\Nand fly away ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.21,0:22:14.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ As a panorama spreads itself\Nthroughout my being ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.35,0:22:19.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ The Earth, having been kicked\Nin the face, gets angry ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.62,0:22:26.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ And makes one of its\Nvolcanoes explode ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.36,0:22:32.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ lf, within the thawed polar ice ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.96,0:22:41.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ There is a dinosaur, then I want\Nto train him to balance atop a ball ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.88,0:22:45.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ Cha-la head cha-la ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.36,0:22:54.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ No matter what may happen, I feel\Nas though nothing can bother me ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.29,0:22:57.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ Cha-la head cha-la ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.43,0:23:01.94,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Next Episode Preview"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.76,0:23:02.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, what's with the next episode\Nof {\i1}Lucky Star{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.80,0:23:04.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Konata here.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.02,0:23:06.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right when I was starting to play\N{\i1}Monster Hunter Dos{\i0},
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.76,0:23:11.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,defeating five Geanos was\Nthe condition to use a weapon,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.24,0:23:14.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I went to the village and had the\Ngathering hall offer me the quest,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.88,0:23:17.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but when I defeated the five Geanos,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.26,0:23:19.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,or even when I plucked so much\NSnow Mountain Grass,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.50,0:23:21.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,even when I gathered\Nso much Poponotan,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.37,0:23:24.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't go back to the village,\Nand that was when I first realized
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.73,0:23:27.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that I had to put it into\Nthe storage box by myself,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.05,0:23:28.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and the fact is that I was\Ngetting less in rewards
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.70,0:23:31.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,all because I didn't read\Nthe user's manual,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.12,0:23:34.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so don't you think that the reason\Nwhy you're not making money
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.84,0:23:37.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is based on what you do in real life?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.36,0:23:40.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next episode: Fixtures of Summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.52,0:23:43.48,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Fixtures of Summer."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.24,0:23:41.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look forward to it!
